        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Israel Sovereignty Reassurance Act of 2021</b> <strong>or ISRA</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits using funds made available to the Department of State for FY2022 to implement, administer, or enforce any policy that rescinds the U.S. recognition of the Golan Heights as part of Israel.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
